Yuvi - Story Aerobics for kids takes your children on an exciting workout adventure through ten beautiful stories. Everyone gets a chance to help Yuvi save all the toys in the world. They were stolen by wizard Zorkus who has hidden them into his enchanted land. The stories are designed in a way that motivates kids to exercise.  They can develop their imagination and motor skills, while having incredible fun. Help your kids stay healthy fit and happy. Join Yuvi on his magical adventure!

Africa
In the first episode Yuvi lands in enchanted Africa, where Zorkus has hidden our balls. To save them he has to face scary birds, hungry lions and a herd of buffalo.
